snippet.title: Send Help | Official Trailer | In Theaters Jan 30
snippet.description:
Rachel McAdams. Dylan O’Brien. SEND HELP.

Directed by Sam Raimi, only in theaters January 30, 2026.

20th Century Studios’ Send Help, the upcoming darkly comedic psychological thriller from genre-bending visionary director Sam Raimi (Spider-Man, The Evil Dead).

The all-original film stars Oscar® and Tony Award® nominated actress Rachel McAdams (Spotlight, Are You There God? It's Me, Margaret., Mean Girls), Dylan O’Brien (Twinless, Saturday Night), Edyll Ismail (La Brea), Dennis Haysbert (Far from Heaven), Xavier Samuel (Elvis), Chris Pang (Crazy Rich Asians), Thaneth Warakulnukroh (Thai Cave Rescue), and Emma Raimi (Happy Pills), and releases in theaters nationwide on January 30, 2026. 

Linda Liddle (Rachel McAdams) and Bradley Preston (Dylan O’Brien), two colleagues who find themselves stranded on a deserted island after they are the only survivors of a plane crash. On the island, they must overcome past grievances and work together to survive, but ultimately, it becomes an unsettling and darkly humorous battle of wills and wits to make it out alive. 

“I’ve always loved stories where interesting, dynamic characters are pushed to extremes,” says director Sam Raimi. “In our story, the power shifts create an escalating situation that’s brimming with unexpected turns and suspense.” 

Send Help is produced by Raimi and Zainab Azizi (65), executive produced by JJ Hook (The Amateur), and written by Damian Shannon & Mark Swift (Friday the 13th, Baywatch), with original music by Danny Elfman (The Nightmare Before Christmas, Batman).

snippet.title: Pretty Woman 2 (2025) - Teaser Trailer | Richard Gere, Julia Roberts
snippet.description:
#prettywoman2 #juliaroberts #richardgere

Julia Roberts and Richard Gere rumored for Pretty Woman 2.

Editing, VFX, SFX, Thumbnail by @KHStudio please subscribe:
✅ YouTube: https://bit.ly/KHstudio

🎥 Attention viewers!

Please note that this video is a concept trailer created solely for artistic and entertainment purposes. I have meticulously incorporated various effects, sound design, AI technologies (Google Veo 3), movie analytics, and other elements to bring my vision to life. Its purpose is purely artistic, aiming to entertain and engage with the YouTube community. My goal is to showcase my creativity and storytelling skills through this trailer. Thank you for your support, and let's dive into the world of imagination! 🍿

💞 Pretty Woman 2

Speculation pictures a warm, contemporary sequel where romance meets real life—second chances, shifting priorities, and the courage to choose each other again. Julia Roberts and Richard Gere are imagined to bring playful chemistry tempered by years and wisdom.

Fans expect upscale L.A. sparkle with grounded emotional stakes: boardrooms, galleries, and late-night diners where hard talks lead to honest laughter. The heart is in the small gestures—hands found, promises kept, and a city that roots for love.

Nothing official yet, but whispers favor a feel-good tone with grown-up complications and a finale that feels celebratory, not fairy-tale perfect. Charming, modern, and a little bit magical.

Feel free to express your thoughts on this exciting project by leaving a comment below.

snippet.title: DUMP - Official Cinematic Trailer
snippet.description:
DUMP comes to Roblox on October 17th, 2025 at 1 PM PT!

Dive into the junkyard, scavenge for rare items, and outsmart everyone to claim the best finds. Whether you’re collecting, building, or stealing, chaos is the only guarantee.

So join the chaos, flex your collection, and rise to the top!

Join the DUMP Roblox Community: https://www.roblox.com/communities/36047290/CayPlay

💬 Discord: https://discord.gg/dumpgame
🐦 X/Twitter: https://x.com/cayplaystudios

Animation & Storyboarding: Vector3
🌐 https://vectorthree.dev/

Music: Epidemic Sound

Trailer Guest Appearances: @KreekCraft @FoltynFamily @steak 

Executive Producers: Travis Richardson & Caylus Cunningham

🎮 ABOUT THE DEVELOPER
CayPlay is an indie game studio co-founded by @caylusblox and Travis Richardson, focused on building creator-led, open-ended games packed with fun and chaos. After the success of Waterpark Simulators EA launch, DUMP is CayPlay’s next big adventure and it’s first Roblox game.

Press Contact: press@cayplay.com
Join the team: jobs@cayplay.com 

No AI was used in the creation of this trailer or game. CayPlay prides itself on being a creator-first studio, built by real people who love making games. Every scene, sound, and idea comes from passionate artists, developers, and storytellers who believe in creativity over shortcuts.

#DUMP #Roblox #CayPlay #Simulator #RobloxGame #CinematicTrailer #IndieGame #Caylus

snippet.title: Rules of Engagement: The Grey State - Official Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Check out the Reveal Trailer for Rules of Engagement: The Grey State, an upcoming free-to-play PvEvP first-person Lovecraftian multiplayer extraction shooter developed by Grey Studio (formerly known as Aurora Studio). Players will explore a supernatural dimension as a Strider hired by an elusive organization to study the unstable dimension known as The Grey State. Race against the clock upon every entry into The Grey State to gather supplies, engage with horrifying monsters of the dimension, and make it out alive. Rules of Engagement: The Grey State is coming to PC (Steam) in 2026.

#IGN #Gaming

Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything — be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer “Capture the Flag” game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. — Attention Viewers ⚠️
— This is a Fan-Made Concept Trailer for:
— KPOP DEMON HUNTERS 2

— This video is a fan-made concept trailer, created solely for artistic and entertainment purposes.The goal behind this trailer is to showcase my creativity and storytelling skills through a concept trailer based on a unique and original idea. By combining various effects, sound design, and AI technologies, I’ve crafted a cinematic experience that reimagines familiar worlds in bold and imaginative ways. This trailer is not official and is intended to entertain, inspire, and engage with the YouTube community. Thank you for your support — now let’s dive into a world shaped by creativity and craft. 🎬✨

— In this concept trailer for KPop Demon Hunters 2, the story continues after the sealing of the Honmoon, as Rumi, Mira, and Zoey face a new kind of darkness born not from demons, but from their own devoted fans. When the Phantom Chorus begins turning admiration into possession, the trio must rediscover the harmony that once saved them, confronting the blurred line between fame and faith. As their music becomes both a weapon and a lifeline, the boundaries between stage and battlefield collapse, forcing them to choose between the spotlight and salvation. Blending emotional resonance with mythic scale, the sequel explores how belief itself can summon angels—or awaken monsters.

snippet.title: Ruzhowa (OFF THE STAGE SESSIONS - Jah Prayzah
snippet.description:
Off The Stage Sessions | Ruzhowa (Acoustic)

Welcome to Off The Stage Sessions, an intimate musical experience where Jah Prayzah strips down his songs to their raw, soulful essence, giving fans the chance to feel the heart of his music away from the noise of the big stage.

Today’s spotlight is on Ruzhowa, a song that carries a deep spiritual message. Ruzhowa means “a hedge”, a protective boundary that keeps one safe. In this song, Jah Prayzah speaks to the divine protection that God places around His people. He asks for success, safeguarding for himself and his generation, and the peace that comes from living under God’s care.

Immerse yourself in this heartfelt acoustic rendition, pure, reflective, and filled with faith.

Credits:
Song Composed by: Mukudzeyi Mukombe
Shot and Edited by: Director Dave
Acoustic Guitar: Adrian Tate
Styling: Wagwizi Closet

snippet.title: The Family Plan 2 — Official Trailer | Apple TV
snippet.description:
Deck the halls, dodge the bad guys. The Morgans are back for The Family Plan 2, this time in Europe. Streaming November 21. https://apple.co/_TheFamilyPlan2

Dan Morgan (Mark Wahlberg) is many things: a devoted husband, a loving father, a celebrated car salesman. He’s also a former assassin. And when his past catches up to his present, he’s forced to take his unsuspecting family (Michelle Monaghan, Zoe Colletti and Van Crosby) on a road trip unlike any other.

The Family Plan 2 is an Apple Original Film hailing from Skydance Media, the sequel to “The Family Plan” will be directed by Simon Cellan Jones. David Ellison, Dana Goldberg and Don Granger will produce for Skydance, alongside Wahlberg and Stephen Levinson through Municipal Pictures. John G. Scotti will executive produce along with Cellan Jones. David Coggeshall, the writer of the first movie, has returned to pen the sequel.

snippet.title: A Merry Little Ex-Mas | Alicia Silverstone & Oliver Hudson | Official Trailer | Netflix
snippet.description:
This holiday season, sometimes the messiest Christmas is the most memorable.
Recently divorced Kate (Alicia Silverstone) is determined to pull off one last perfect family holiday before selling her beloved home. But when her ex-husband Everett (Oliver Hudson) shows up with his younger, picture-perfect new girlfriend, Kate’s holiday dream spirals into chaos. With comedy, heart, and plenty of holiday drama, A Merry Little Ex-Mas also stars Jameela Jamil, Pierson Fodé, and Melissa Joan Hart, directed by Steve Carr.

Watch on Netflix: https://www.netflix.com/title/81735104

About Netflix:
Netflix is one of the world's leading entertainment services, with over 300 million paid memberships in over 190 countries enjoying TV series, films and games across a wide variety of genres and languages. Members can play, pause and resume watching as much as they want, anytime, anywhere, and can change their plans at any time.

A Merry Little Ex-Mas | Alicia Silverstone & Oliver Hudson | Official Trailer | Netflix

All Kate and Everett want for Christmas is an amicable divorce and one last holiday as a family, but new flames and old feelings complicate their plans.

snippet.title: THE RUNNING MAN Comic-Con Trailer (2026) Josh Brolin, New Sci-Fi Action Movies 4K
snippet.description:
🏃‍♂️ The Running Man (2025) – Official Synopsis & Lore Breakdown

In a future where fear is televised and freedom is a game, survival is the prize.

📖 Synopsis:
The Running Man (2025) reimagines the cult classic for a modern audience, delivering a high-octane dystopian thriller where society is controlled by media manipulation and authoritarian rule. When a former soldier is falsely accused and forced into a brutal televised deathmatch, he must navigate a gauntlet of deadly hunters and twisted viewers who see death as entertainment.

📌 Key Details:

🎬 Genre: Sci-Fi Thriller, Dystopian Action
💥 Tone: Darker, more grounded than the 1987 version
🌐 Setting: Mega-cities, underground resistance zones, dystopian arenas
